{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-06-10-1",
 "title": "Watching the Pallandos Race",
 "summary": "Fresh off his own rookie run, the disguised agent Bazil McKenzie (as the swooper Mege Vauki) climbs into the stands at the Reckless Abandon Swoop Arena to watch a race, joined by his new acquaintance, the speed-loving Meditersarian Luther Syss. The two cheer through a brutal multi-terrain race dominated by the Caspian Pallando twins, Whitney and Ernie, with Altair Quila -- mocked by the announcer as Nature Girl -- battling back aboard the mud-caked Achernar. Bazil, recognizing Quila, abandons rooting for Ernie and bellows her on at the top of his lungs, drawing odd looks, while the diplomat Eva Sargent slips in for a break only to grow more anxious as the racers crash. The race ends in spectacular wreckage at the dianoga sewer, with both Pallandos hurled from their swoops as medteams rush to collect them.",
